#: polling_stations/templates/fragments/keep_safe.html:4
msgid "Keeping you and fellow voters safe!"
msgstr "Yn eich cadw chi a'ch cyd-bleidleiswyr yn ddiogel!"

#: polling_stations/templates/fragments/keep_safe.html:5
msgid ""
"Local election teams will be doing everything they can to ensure voting in "
"person on polling day is safe for everyone. This means there will be safety "
"measures in place at polling stations to prevent the spread of COVID-19, "
"many of which you’ll be very familiar with! "
msgstr ""
"Bydd timau etholiad lleol yn gwneud popeth y gallant i sicrhau bod "
"pleidleisio mewn person ar ddiwrnod yr etholiad yn ddiogel i bawb. Golyga "
"hynny y bydd yna fesurau diogelwch yn eu lle mewn gorsafoedd pleidleisio er "
"mwyn atal lledaeniad COVID-19, nifer yr ydych eisoes yn gyfarwydd â hwy!"

#: polling_stations/templates/fragments/keep_safe.html:8
msgid ""
"There will be a limit to the number of people allowed in a polling station "
"at any given time to allow for <strong>social distancing</strong>."
msgstr ""
"Bydd nifer cyfyngedig o bobl yn cael bod mewn gorsaf bleidleisio ar unrhyw "
"adeg er mwyn gallu cadw <strong>pellter cymdeithasol</strong>."

#: polling_stations/templates/fragments/keep_safe.html:9
msgid ""
"Please remember your <strong>face covering</strong> - you will need this to "
"enter the polling station and will be expected to wear it throughout."
msgstr ""
"Cofiwch eich <strong>gorchudd wyneb</strong> - bydd angen hwn arnoch i fynd "
"i mewn i'r orsaf bleidleisio a bydd disgwyl i chi ei wisgo yr holl amser."

#: polling_stations/templates/fragments/keep_safe.html:10
msgid ""
"Make sure to <strong>sanitise your hands</strong> before and after voting. "
"In many places, sanitiser will be available but it may be a good idea to "
"carry your own!"
msgstr ""
"Sicrhewch eich bod yn <strong>diheintio eich dwylo</strong> cyn ac ar ôl "
"pleidleisio. Mewn nifer o leoedd, bydd diheintydd ar gael ond gallai fod yn "
"syniad da dod â rhai eich hun!"

#: polling_stations/templates/fragments/keep_safe.html:11
msgid ""
"Some polling stations will supply clean pencils for voters but it may be "
"best to bring your own with you."
msgstr ""
"Bydd rhai gorsafoedd pleidleisio yn darparu pensiliau glan ar gyfer "
"pleidleiswyr ond gallai fod yn well dod ag un eich hun."

#: polling_stations/templates/fragments/keep_safe.html:12
msgid ""
"Polling Stations will be cleaned regularly by polling staff. You may need to "
"wait while a booth is sanitised before you enter."
msgstr ""
"Bydd Gorsafoedd Pleidleisio'n cael eu glanhau'n rheolaidd gan staff. Mae'n "
"bosib y bydd angen i chi aros tra bod bwth yn cael ei lanhau cyn i chi fynd "
"i mewn."

#: polling_stations/templates/fragments/keep_safe.html:13
msgid ""
"Polling Station staff may be working behind safety screens - this doesn’t "
"mean you can’t <strong>ask for assistance if you require it!</strong>"
